snippet: The two-time champion Cristie Kerr shot a five-under-par 66 to take a two-stroke lead through the third round of the L.P.G.A. Tour’s Kingsmill Championship.
abstract: Two-time champion Cristie Kerr takes third-round lead at LPGA Tour’s Kingsmill Championship; other golf results noted.
lead_paragraph: The two-time champion Cristie Kerr shot a five-under-par 66 to take a two-stroke lead through the third round of the L.P.G.A. Tour’s Kingsmill Championship.
